                <mxCell id="s10-desc" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Build &amp; push the API image&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0,0,0), rgb(255,255,255));&quot;&gt;GitHub Actions (OIDC, no static keys) builds the Docker image and pushes it to ECR.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=-4;fontSize=14;labelBackgroundColor=none;whiteSpace=wrap;fontFamily=Helvetica;" parent="s10-grp" vertex="1">
